Package com.ultreon.mods.lib.core.block.fluid

Interface FluidRecipe<C extends FluidInventory>

Type Parameters:
C - The inventory type
All Superinterfaces:
net.minecraft.world.item.crafting.Recipe<C>
public interface FluidRecipe<C extends FluidInventory> extends net.minecraft.world.item.crafting.Recipe<C>
An Recipe which can use fluids as ingredients or results. Can also handle items if needed. Also see FluidInventory and FluidIngredient.

All the fluid-related input/output methods return a list. If these do not apply to the recipe type, you should return an empty list.
